title: Looking For Players to make a Diamond+ team for comps and OOL

embed.description: Hey guys its Damian here. Im guessing you are here to apply your details to join a team that will hopefully play in the OOL and higher. Along with this other competitions that are happening in OCE.

body:
Hey guys,
My names Damian and I am wanting to manage a team in OCE to play competitions and compete in the OOL so we can hopefully make it big. If you are interested please message me on league and apply in the application link provided. Already have some high diamond to challenger players that are interested. If you believe you are fit to start playing competitive please apply.
Thanks.
